qas.question: What is the population growth rate of Somerset county

answers.text: Population growth is higher than the national average, with a 6.4% increase, in the Somerset County Council area, since 1991, and a 17% increase since 1981

qas.question: The unemployment rate of the county

answers.text: the unemployment rate is lower than the regional and national average.

qas.question: What percentage of the population is economically active

answers.text: is higher than the regional and national average
